  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -3.486453747686696        -94.8712         -2187.78         -9153.68
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.200234744066832          5.4487           125.65           525.72
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.255830552312394         -6.9615          -160.54          -671.68
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
